job_detail:
This position belongs to Tag - Moni Media BU
此崗位隸屬於新加坡商泰意有限公司台灣分公司的Moni Media業務部門

Job Responsibilities:
- Develop new business relationships and generate new revenue;
-探索發展新的業務關係，為公司帶來新的業務增長；
- Actively generate and close new business leads;
-積極開發和關閉新的商機；
- Achieve quarterly sales quota from inbound and proactive pipeline targets;
-根據設立的目標和渠道完成季度銷售額；
- Represent company to maintain potential clients;
-代表公司與潛在客戶維持良好關係；
- Create client proposals and quotations with accurate information, process and structure;
-用準確的信息，流程和結構為客戶提供提案和報價；
- Respond and manage the tender and RFP processes;
-響應和管理招標，RFP流程；
- Be a key contact point for contracted clients and internal stake holders.
-成爲簽約客戶和内部對接窗口的關鍵聯係人。
